From horsepower to #GenZ superpower!
Had the absolute pleasure of hosting a vibrant meet-and-greet with 40 brilliant young minds from The Lit School @thelitschool at our BBT Bangalore showroom. These future content powerhouses brought a wave of fresh perspective, unfiltered creativity, and unstoppable energy. While I shared my journey in the world of content and luxury cars, I walked away with insights, trends, and inspiration from this next-gen creator tribe.
Here’s to learning, unlearning, and always evolving — together!

#BBTBangalore #thelitschool #genzcreators #contentmeetscarlove #bigboytoysindia #ritikaahuja #creatorcommunity #luxurycars #queensdriveclub

An afternoon immersed in luxury, heritage, and craftsmanship.
Thrilled to have hosted an exclusive Hermès Masterclass, beautifully led by @puraskar from Elite Magazine, known for sourcing Hermès treasures from across the world for elite clientele.
From decoding iconic styles to exploring rare colors and customizations, it was a journey into the artistry that defines Hermès.
Proud that Queen’s Drive Club continues to create such meaningful collaborations, offering our members deeper experiences into the world of true luxury.

latestPosts.caption:
Unlocking the secrets of Hermès — one stitch, one story at a time.
ELITE Magazine, along with Essentia Homes, Queens Drive Club & Rimadesio, hosted the exclusive Hermès De-Coded Masterclass.
From the legacy of the Birkin to the elegance of the Kelly, guests explored the craftsmanship, forms, and finesse behind the world's most coveted bags.
Curated and presented by Puraskar Thadani @puraskar , Editor of ELITE Magazine — a true celebration of timeless luxury.

#EliteMagazine #HermesDecoded #BirkinLove #KellyObsession #LuxuryUnlocked #EssentiaHomes #QueensDriveClub #Rimadesio

A surreal moment for the Queens Drive Club as we stepped into the Parliament of India—where the soul of our democracy resides. Walking through these historic corridors filled our hearts with pride, purpose, and patriotism. It’s not just a visit, it’s a reminder that women belong in every room where decisions are made. Grateful for this honour and hopeful for the change we continue to drive.
